                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120916-60-off338 t18120916-60-cd339"></join>, a jacket, value 1 l. three waistcoats, value 26 s. six pair of trowsers, value 2 l. 12 s. five shirts, value 2 l. three pair of stockings, value 6 s. an handkerchief, value 2 s. a pair of braces, value 1 s. and a broach, value 16 s.
            </rs> the property of 
